with her as I recall.

13:43.455 --> 13:47.693
- Well, Val was nice to me and
she tried to get to know me.

13:48.694 --> 13:50.129
- I didn't try?

13:51.497 --> 13:52.998
I mean, what--

13:54.333 --> 13:55.868
What about
all the good things I did?

13:57.002 --> 13:59.572
I bought your prom dress,
and your textbooks.

13:59.672 --> 14:01.240
The piano lessons.

