of things you could do

14:13.152 --> 14:16.422
to not be considered
the absolute worst dad.

14:18.424 --> 14:19.725
- Hm.

14:21.894 --> 14:24.029
- And I know some of that
is on my mom.

14:24.096 --> 14:25.865
I do.

14:25.931 --> 14:28.834
But even when you were around,
you were a selfish asshole.

14:28.901 --> 14:31.871
And now you are sleeping
with her,

14:31.937 --> 14:33.873
and you're confusing her,

14:33.939 --> 14:36.375
and I'm fucking caught
in the middle of it again.

14:48.053 --> 14:49.388
- I was an asshole.

14:50.589 --> 14:52.892
